<plot>This documentary contains, in its entirety, the military press briefing given by General H. Norman Schwarzkopf just after the end of the Persian Gulf War in 1991. General Schwarzkopf describes in detail the military tactics that enabled Coalition forces to liberate Kuwait from Iraqi occupation. Afterward, expert commentary on the briefing is provided by ABC News military analysts.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?481200</url></doc>
